{
  "stem": "20686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was all premeditated, and also this was a plan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- I called it-- they-- they are planning chaos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They planned chaos.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's what they did, and it worked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they lined up men separate and women separate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And everybody had to lift up their hand like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Over.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they have to mention only your age and how old you are.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And according to this, we were given-- it was life or death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If you're over the limit, so, you know--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I describe it again in my poem, Of which this is the best-- the best sort of, to me, perhaps. 'On the thirteenth date of the month, after a journey of tears and sweat, my family and I arrived to Germany's kingdom of death.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember our last embrace, mother breaking down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What will happen to the children?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Will I ever see you, my son?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, I know what happened to the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know what became of them all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to keep what's left of my sanity, there are scenes I refuse to recall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The scene is in stony bunker, the last plea for breath, the smell of gas, the eerie silence, dead.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] But in the night, day, where the pit is still aflame, I hear them calling my name-- my name, my shame.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I once had a mother and father, two sisters in their prime of life-- Ida the gentle dove, and Pola, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I also had two nieces, little girls of six and four, one with a windowless basement, the other with a lock on the door.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, they are only ashes and an everlasting sigh.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the twilight house, a mother's cry.' That's how it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's no exaggerations here.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
